HEADWORD: Zolaism
<hw>Zo"la*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The literary
theories and practices of the French novelist <person>Emile
<etsep>Zola</etsep></person> (1840-1902); naturalism, esp. in a
derogatory sense.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Zo"la*ist</wf>, <pos>n.</pos>
-- <wf>Zo`la*is"tic</wf> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> --
<wf>Zo"la*ize</wf> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
